  "description": "FAT-II scripture enforced at maximum: bitDepth 0.0 = 4-bit destruction. 16 possible amplitude values. Every transient a staircase. Every sustain a quantization hum raised to satDrive 0.95. Noise at 0.8. Filter resonance 0.88 — the ladder screams at the staircase. This is not lo-fi aesthetic. This is lo-fi as weapon. The whale in a blender.",
